title: Louis Vuitton New Wave PM
description: Louis Vuitton New Wave PM in black chevron and wave quilted calfskin leather (year 2019). Featuring aged gold-tone hardware, removable top handle embossed with multicoloured Vuitton lettering, and sliding chain shoulder strap. The push-lock closure opens to a black microfibre interior with a patch pocket. Approximate dimensions: 23cm(L) x 14cm(H) x 5.5cm(D), handle drop 5cm, strap drop 53cm. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
